videos.description: Florida's Luke Del Rio avoids multiple defenders and finds DeAndre Goolsby for 25 yards in the first quarter.
videos.headline: Gators' Del Rio avoids defenders to find receiver

videos.description: Lamical Perine finds a gap and gets the Gator's first touchdown.
videos.headline: Gators strike first

videos.description: Commodores' quarterback Kyle Shurmur finds  Kalija Lipscomb in the end zone for the 13-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Vanderbilt's Lipscomb makes great catch for TD

videos.description: Gator's Lamical Perine runs 13 yards for the touchdown. Perine's second touchdown of the game.
videos.headline: Florida's Perine dodges defense for TD

videos.description: Commodores' Kyle Shurmur finds Caleb Scott wide open for his first catch and touchdown of the season.
videos.headline: Vanderbilt's Scott wide open in end zone for TD

videos.description: Luke Del Rio  is sacked by Jonathan Wynn, and hit hard on the next play by Dare Odeyingbo. Del Rio would leave the game for the  locker room.
videos.headline: Back-to-back hits sends Gator's QB Del Rio to locker room

videos.description: Vanderbilt's quarterback Kyle Shurmur connects with Donaven Tennyson for a great catch.
videos.headline: Commodores' QB makes great throw for 35-yard gain

videos.description: Florida's Feleipe Franks lobs the ball to Tyrie Cleveland who makes the grab in double coverage which leads to a Gators field goal.
videos.headline: Gators' Cleveland makes 49 yard grab

videos.description: Jim McElwain says Feleipe Franks is doing exactly what they want him to do, and how they need to do a better job settling down.
videos.headline: Gators' coach McElwain discusses backup QB's performance

videos.description: Florida's Malik Davis pushes through the defense and reaches out for a Gator touchdown.
videos.headline: Gator's take lead with Davis' TD

videos.description: Florida's Freddie Swain catches the ball with one hand after it was deflected by a Vanderbilt player.
videos.headline: Gators' Swain makes impressive catch off deflection

videos.description: Florida's Lamical Perine is pushed by temmates into the end zone for a one-yard touchdown in the fourth quarter.
videos.headline: Gators' push Perine into the end zone for TD

videos.description: Devin Cochran falls like a tree after barely being touched by Cece Jefferson on the offsides play.
videos.headline: Vanderbilt's lineman takes a tumble

videos.description: Florida's Cece Jefferson flies into the backfield to tackle Vanderbilt's Khari Blasingame.
videos.headline: Gator's Jefferson lights up Vanderbilt player

videos.description: Commodores' Kyle Shurmur completes the pass to Nathan Marcus for a seven-yard touchdown,
videos.headline: Shurmer finds Marcus in the end zone to close the gap

videos.description: Gator's Malik Davis breaks away from the defense and runs 39 yards for a touchdown.
videos.headline: Florida's Davis stays on his feet for TD

videos.description: Florida head coach Jim McElwain is happy with back-up quarterback Feleipe Franks' performance.
videos.headline: McElwain impressed with Gators' fight against Vandy

videos.description: Backup quarterback Feleipe Franks discusses getting the win against Vanderbilt after replacing injured starting quarterback Luke Del Rio.
videos.headline: Gators' Franks discusses getting a win off the bench

videos.description: ESPN's Greg McElroy and Dave Pasch discuss Feleipe Franks performance and Florida's running game in the Gators' 38-24 win over the Commodores.
videos.headline: Gators run away with win against Vanderbilt
